// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0504 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: dda2c8d0-c9ae-58a3-90f4-a1a4b970f49c

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
